Seller to offer a 2-1 Rate Buydown with seller acceptable offer. 

Spacious Cul-de-Sac Residence in Victoria Lakes, Overlooking a Serene Pond. This home features a generous great room that seamlessly flows into an open breakfast area, kitchen, dining room, and foyer. The master bedroom suite boasts ample space and a walk-in closet, while two guest bedrooms share access to an additional full bathroom. Whether you are looking for a home to entertain or looking for a place to start your family, this is the one! Schedule your tour today!
